Come on, we want to see your ugly mug, the first time I saw Ed's picture was on a milk carton. He put on a Marine Corps Dress Blue Jacket and took the picture himself and send it in, just so that girls would began to look for him.<br><br>
I remember the first time I spoke before a group of people about Vietnam. I got their attention by saying, &quot;I shot and killed more enemy soldiers in Vietnam, then are here today.&quot; It was in a church.<br><br>
Kids in school are different, little boys still admire the warrior soldier. They want to hear about Vietnam from those that were there. Vietnam is a war they know nothing about. Do us proud tomorrow, little PP. <br><br>

